text:
Do you like searching through boxes? Finding a ad date: 10/03/2015 
Do you like searching through boxes? Finding a treasure? Have a knack for knickknacks? A passion for pricing? The Coastal Hospice Market is seeking volunteers for our newly opened thrift store located at 29813 Colvin Street in Gold Beach. Days and hours vary. If you want to help support hospice services in Curry County by joining our team please contact Marilyn at 541-373-3477 or stop by the store for more details. The Mission of Coastal Home Health & Hospice is providing compassionate care to enhance the quality of life in the communities we serve.
